### tracker 목록 조회
GET {{host}}/tracker

### tracker 단건 조회
GET {{host}}/tracker/1

### tracker 생성
POST {{host}}/tracker
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"name": "appsflyer",
	"tracking_url": "https://app.appsflyer.com/com.example.app",
	"install_postback_url": "https://backend.example.com/appsflyer/install",
	"event_postback_url": "https://backend.example.com/appsflyer/event"
}

### tracker 수정 — 전체 교체 방식 (4개 필드 모두 필요)
PATCH {{host}}/tracker/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"name": "adjust",
	"tracking_url": "https://app.adjust.com/abc123",
	"install_postback_url": "https://backend.example.com/adjust/install",
	"event_postback_url": "https://backend.example.com/adjust/event"
}

### tracker 삭제
DELETE {{host}}/tracker/1
